(2, 'Ho tara aminao foana', '[00:17.38]Ilay fijerinao iny malala tena tiako,\r\n[00:22.25]Miampy ilay fitsikinao kely toa manjopiaka,\r\n[00:26.98]Ka za manahy fa ho taratara aminao foana aho,\r\n[00:30.60]Na ho dimy na ho zato taona,\r\n[00:32.84]Fenoiko hafanana raha sendra hatsiaka.\r\n[00:37.51]Dia aza miahiahy fa ho ataoko henika raha fitia,\r\n[00:44.18]Hofenoiko hamamiana ny fitiavan-dry,\r\n[00:48.14]Dia aza manahy fa tsy handanindany fotoana aho,\r\n[00:51.88]Sanatria ny hanadala anao,\r\n[00:54.93]Ny hirariana tsy hisy tomiaka.\r\n[00:58.60]Mety handalo rahona, hisy hisompatra ilay fitia,\r\n[01:03.76]Fa tsy ataoko ahasakana ahy raha ny fitiavako an-dry,\r\n[01:08.61]Fa miara-miafy dia miara-tafa any aoriana,\r\n[01:12.04]Ny fiarahantsika ho feno hamamiana,\r\n[01:15.21]Isika sy ianao samy hankafy,\r\n[01:19.12]Tsy avelako ianao na inon-kidona n\'inon-kihatra,\r\n[01:24.27]Amen be fa ny tanjontsika tsy maintsy ho tratra,\r\n[01:29.15]Hoe hiara-tanora dia hiara antitra,\r\n[01:32.03]Ho sambatra mandrakizay ry tiako ah,\r\n[01:35.59]Ny fitiavanao sarobidy ho ahy.\r\n[01:39.86]Dia any aoriana any hanana harena izaho sy ianao,\r\n[01:44.65]Dia ireo zanatsika anie ho mamy kely mitovy aminao,\r\n[01:49.60]Hangalana kely amin\'ny anaranao dia apetraka eo koa ny ahy,\r\n[01:56.31]Efa tsy andriko sahady izay fotoana izay,\r\n[02:00.31]Dia apetratsika anatrehan\'ny Avo ny fitiavantsika,\r\n[02:05.22]Ho lavitra ankaso ho feno hafanana tsy mety hangatatsiaka,\r\n[02:10.31]Dia aza manahy fa mbola ho tara aminao foana na amin\'izany andro izany ry tiako ah,\r\n[02:16.79]Fa ianao anie sarobidy ho ahy.\r\n[02:20.77]Mety handalo rahona, hisy hisompatra ilay fitia,\r\n[02:25.85]Fa tsy ataoko ahasakana ahy raha ny fitiavako an-dry,\r\n[02:30.76]Fa miara-miafy dia miara-tafa any aoriana,\r\n[02:34.38]Ny fiarahantsika ho feno hamamiana,\r\n[02:37.42]Isika sy ianao samy hankafy,\r\n[02:41.23]Tsy avelako ianao na inon-kidona n\'inon-kihatra,\r\n[02:46.25]Amen be fa ny tanjontsika tsy maintsy ho tratra,\r\n[02:51.49]Hoe hiara-tanora dia hiara antitra,\r\n[02:54.87]Ho sambatra mandrakizay ry tiako ah,\r\n[02:58.07]Ny fitiavanao sarobidy ho ahy.\r\n[03:02.16]Tsy avelako ianao na inon-kidona na inon-kihatra,\r\n[03:06.91]Amen be fa ny tanjontsika tsy maintsy ho tratra.', 3),
